The body of a 50-year oldwoman was found dumped at a cemetery at Wiyoni area, Lamu island, on Friday morning.It is believed that Anne Wangari was waylaid and gang-raped before she was killed.Deputy county commissioner Benard Tanui said the mother of four could have been murdered elsewhere and her body dumped in the area. We are investigating the matter and hope to arrest her killers soon, said Tanui.He warned locals against taking the law into their own hands and engaging in crime.The body was taken to Mpeketoni sub-county hospital mortuary.